"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"The US president wants China to open up more, while China is expected to talk to Trump about Taiwan. China welcomed US President Donald Trump with cheering children and a troop parade before a long meeting with Xi-Jinping.\",            \"english_title\": \"US and China Talks\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de EE.UU. quiere que China se abra m\u00e1s, mientras que se espera que China hable con Trump sobre Taiw\u00e1n. China dio la bienvenida al presidente de EE.UU. Donald Trump con ni\u00f1os animando y un desfile de tropas antes de una larga reuni\u00f3n con Xi-Jinping.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Conversaciones entre EE.UU. y China\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Drones that were going to Russia crashed in Latvia last week, causing political problems.\",            \"english_title\": \"Drones Crash in Latvia\",            \"translated_version\": \"Drones que iban a Rusia se estrellaron en Letonia la semana pasada, causando problemas pol\u00edticos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Drones se Estrellan en Letonia\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Eight children died after air strikes hit the south of Beirut.\",            \"english_title\": \"Air Strikes in Beirut\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ocho ni\u00f1os murieron despu\u00e9s de ataques a\u00e9reos en el sur de Beirut.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataques A\u00e9reos en Beirut\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A 12-year-old girl was among those killed after Russia attacked Ukraine overnight, officials say.\",            \"english_title\": \"Russia Attacks Ukraine\",            \"translated_version\": \"Una ni\u00f1a de 12 a\u00f1os estaba entre los muertos despu\u00e9s de que Rusia atac\u00f3 Ucrania durante la noche, dicen los oficiales.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Rusia Ataca Ucrania\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Rebel fighters and Rwandan troops are accused of committing crimes after taking over the DR Congo city of Uvira in December.\",            \"english_title\": \"Crimes in DR Congo\",            \"translated_version\": \"Luchadores rebeldes y tropas de Ruanda son acusados de cometer cr\u00edmenes despu\u00e9s de tomar la ciudad de Uvira en el Congo en diciembre.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Cr\u00edmenes en el Congo\"        }    ]}"